name: Mochi
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en: Mochi is a coordination game that utilizes agile principles to reward and punish DAOs and remote-first teams. Play Mochi to set goals, form teams, share insights, & distribute tokens autonomously. Spend less time coordinating in Discord/Slack and get more stuff done.
